<h2 class="text-center"><span class="red-dot">•</span> New Era <span class="red-dot">•</span></h2>
<div class="container mt-3">
  <div class="row">
    <div class="explanation col-6">
      <p>Create a new era by adding a <span class="bold">name</span>, <span class="bold">description</span>, <span class="bold">start date</span> and <span class="bold">end date</span>.</p>
      <div class="tips">
        <h6>Tips<span class="red">:</span></h6>
        <ul>
          <li>Eras should have a <span class="bold">start date</span> and <span class="bold"> an end date</span>.</li>
          <li>Give a <span class="bold">clear name</span>, and keep it as short as possible.</li>
          <li>Write a concise <span class="bold">description</span> of your era that is no longer than <span class="bold">150 characters</span>.</li>
        </ul>
      </div>
    </div>
    <div class="newtimelineform col-6">
      <%= simple_form_for([ @era]) do |f| %>
        <div class="form-inputs">
          <%= f.input :name %>
          <%= f.input :description %>
          <%= f.input :start_date, as: :date%>
          <%= f.input :end_date,as: :date %>
          <%= f.submit class: "submit-btn", value: "Create" %>
        </div>
      <% end %>
    </div>
  </div>
</div>
